      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at old photos today. it’s weird. i don't even recognize that person anymore. not just the face, but the actual soul of them. it feels like that person died a long time ago and i’ve just been walking around in their clothes ever since. like i'm just a ghost or a walking corpse.",
